# Shared Folder for Cartesian Development
# x-systemd.automount: Mounts automatically on first access.
# x-systemd.idle-timeout=60: Unmounts after 60s of inactivity.
# x-systemd.mount-timeout=10: Prevents boot hang if share is missing.

